OL,3,CFormer UK residents living abroad to
OL,4,Cpay more under pension changes
OL,6,FUK expats living abroad will face
OL,7,Fhigher pension payments after the
OL,8,FChancellor tightened the rules on
OL,9,Fcontributions.
OL,11,FThe changes, announced by Rachel
OL,12,FReeves during last week's Budget, will
OL,13,Finclude UK residents looking to move
OL,14,Fto the Channel Islands.
