OL,3,CFormer UK residents living abroad to
OL,4,Cpay more under pension changes
OL,6,FWhile the rise is significant, Timothy
OL,7,FTownsend, Head of Wealth Management
OL,8,Fand Corporate Consulting at
OL,9,FAlexforbes, says the investment is
OL,10,Fstill worthwhile for people who can
OL,11,Fafford the contributions.
OL,13,FHe explains: "It used to be a must
OL,14,Fcontribution, since it was a
OL,15,Frelatively low cost on an annual
OL,16,Fbasis, but now it's going to cost
OL,17,Fmore, so you need to consider it
OL,18,Fclosely."
OL,20,FThe current full UK state pension is
OL,21,Faround #12,000 per year.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/7
