OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F384A1764681722
OL,3,CFormer UK residents living abroad to
OL,4,Cpay more under pension changes
OL,6,FMr Townsend added: "It's still
OL,7,Fsensible and a part of your overall
OL,8,Fretirement plan, but it's not your
OL,9,Fonly retirement plan.
OL,11,F"We are living for longer, so it could
OL,12,Fbe that you get the money back and it
OL,13,Fmay be quite a lucrative investment
OL,14,Ffor some people."
OL,16,FMeanwhile, Carl Walker, Chairman of
OL,17,Fthe Jersey Consumer Council, believes
OL,18,Fthe changes will close what was "a
OL,19,Fvery lucrative loophole" under the
OL,20,Fexisting rules.
