OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F384A1764681722
OL,3,CFormer UK residents living abroad to
OL,4,Cpay more under pension changes
OL,6,FHe adds: "Now, it's not quite an
OL,7,Fattractive prospect as it once was."
OL,9,FMr Walker advises expats to check
OL,10,Ftheir pension with HMRC online and see
OL,11,Fhow many years of contributions are
OL,12,Fremaining, calculate how much it costs
OL,13,Fto buy these years back, and then find
OL,14,Fout how long this will take to return
OL,15,Finto profit.
OL,17,FIn the UK Budget unveiled in spring,
OL,18,Fthe rules around buying back years
OL,19,Fwere altered.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/7
