OL,3,CFormer UK residents living abroad to
OL,4,Cpay more under pension changes
OL,6,FPreviously, those paying into the
OL,7,Fstate pension could purchase up to 18
OL,8,Fyears, but this was reduced to six.
OL,10,FMr Walker warns that from April next
OL,11,Fyear, buying back these years will
OL,12,Fmost likely be charged at the new rate.
OL,14,FHe also adds that those living abroad
OL,15,Fand already paying into the UK state
OL,16,Fpension will not be impacted by the
OL,17,Flatest changes.
OL,19,FMr Walker explains: "Anyone who's in
OL,20,Fthe scheme under the old terms and
OL,21,Fconditions stays in that scheme.
